title: Young Dolph Interveiw and more

description:
Wednesday 11/15- Today on the show we had Young Dolph stop by where he spoke about resentment towards his parents, being shot and definitely let us know that he still got beef with Yo Gotti. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Lebron James after he called himself "King of New York" and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee", with one listener that did not know how to control her anger.
